      <title>摘抄by「千脑智能」</title>
      <link>https://www.samrainhan.com/posts/2024-10-29-excerpt-by-a-thousand-brains-a-new-theory-of-intelligence/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 10:05:48 +0800</pubDate>
